e, I hope, will be able to play next year with me, the poor pet. Come, let us start. The present series belongs to the shadow-and-shine group, two of which I’m going to show you.”

“I see,” said Van.

“You will in a moment,” rejoined the pretty prig. “First of all we must find a nice stick.”

“Look,” said Van, still smarting a bit, “there goes another haw-haw finch.”

